AB  - We re-examine the connection between limited liability, contractual form and the agricultural tenancy ladder in a model with only labor moral hazard. We show that ex post limited liability does not explain sharecropping in this model, but that ex ante limited liability can do so. We characterize the nature of the tenancy ladder in either case.
